{"tid":912041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《後生仔》KOL去台慶冇星味 網民：X！以為係中學雞Grad Din！","createTime":"2018-11-22T11:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T12:04:22.000Z","uid":147522,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab15c302d74bfb4b890343e70c5f3e1a1d13825","tid":912041,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:07:24.000Z","msg":"今年無綫50+1台慶，除了袁偉豪、黃智雯齊奪雙料視帝、視后外，最爆當然係馮盈盈真空行紅地氈搶盡風頭！而台慶咁大件事，一班大家都未必記得名的《＃後生仔傾吓偈》KOL亦奉命出鏡充撐場面，不過就有網民笑佢哋「似足中學生去畢業聚餐」、「一點星味也沒有」學人扮明星咁話！<br />\n<br />\n剛過去的星期一為TVB台慶大日子，全台上下藝人盛裝出席，逼爆舞台，一眾主持人當然企最前排，至於其他藝人的企位&hellip;&hellip; 就視乎你身份地位啦！農夫〈風生水起〉歌詞都有講啦，有啲人係「頒獎典禮裡面 鏡頭唔影呢面 觀眾睇我唔見&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n不過日前就有網民喺討論區表示，一班大家都未必記得名的《＃後生仔傾吓偈》KOL原來亦奉命到台慶充撐場面，真係唔睇IG都唔知原來佢哋有份去，仲鬧爆佢哋衣著奇差，學人扮明星咁話！大家覺得係咪真係咁差呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7qrzR6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7qrzR6.png&h=5cf572aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce35e6b9b134180e741a24b1dcfc7e5eb336037","tid":912041,"uid":74295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d848a4547f9d75ab9c437a4bd3d967230ff1290f","tid":912041,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cef59c2c4d3c93d8e02de23864371be33af616e","tid":912041,"uid":214692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"on99以為自己明星想喧賓奪主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff99148ea7a62766574c03f88b4dbf704b657ef","tid":912041,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"無線平時搵佢地排J2 airtime啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a80a4d